I've never used MATHCAD, so no, I don't have any plans at present to
develop a MATHCAD interface. Sounds like a good project for a someone
who uses both Cantera and MATHCAD... (Since Cantera is open source, the
code I wrote for MATLAB interfacing is part of the source distribution,
and might serve as a guide for developing other interfaces.)
